Requirements     
\layout Itemize

GNU make is MANDATORY in ALL Systems, even if you use a different  compiler.
 
\layout Itemize

On all platforms zlib is now needed since the core uses it.
 If you don't have zlib, a stripped version is included with xmame.
 See: 
\begin_inset LatexCommand \ref[FAQ: Why do I get gz_open symbol not while compiling?]{gzopen}

\end_inset 

 and 
\begin_inset LatexCommand \ref[FAQ: Why do I get zlib.h not found?]{zlib}

\end_inset 


